'''= voluntary state-like organizations responsible for basic functions of social life'''

Concept proposed by [[Franz Nahrada]].

==Description==

Franz Nahrada:

"territorieal LMOs (Life Maintainance Organisations) which are text-exempt and privileged for
taking over essential structural functions, yet organized around some
state-controlled principles that allow individuals to switch and many
other features which go beyond old "clanism". 

